ARTICLE-225: ILLEGAL-BUSINESS-ACTS ∧ MARKET-DISRUPTION;
  CIRC=SERIOUS ⇒ PENALTY=≤5Y IMPRISONMENT/DETENTION ∧ FINE=100–500% ILLEGAL-INCOME;
  CIRC=PARTICULARLY-SERIOUS ⇒ PENALTY=≥5Y IMPRISONMENT ∧ FINE=100–500% ILLEGAL-INCOME OR PROPERTY-CONFISCATION
  ACT1: MONOPOLY-BUSINESS/MONOPOLIZED-COMMODITIES (LAW/ADMIN-CONTROLLED) TRADE WITHOUT-PERMIT
  ACT2: UNAUTHORIZED TRADE IN IMPORT-EXPORT-LICENSES/CERTIFICATES-OF-ORIGIN/OPERATION-PERMITS
  ACT3: OTHER ILLEGAL-BUSINESS-ACTS THAT SERIOUSLY-DISRUPT MARKET-ORDER

ARTICLE-226: VIOLENCE/COERCION FORCES OTHERS TO PURCHASE/SELL COMMODITIES OR PROVIDE/ACCEPT SERVICES;
  PENALTY=≤3Y IMPRISONMENT/DETENTION; CIRC=SERIOUS ⇒ OPTIONAL-FINE

ARTICLE-227:
  CLAUSE1: FORGE/PROFIT FORGED TRAIN/SHIP-TICKETS/STAMPS/OTHER-VALUABLE-COUPONS;
    AMOUNT=RELATIVELY-LARGE ⇒ PENALTY=≤2Y IMPRISONMENT/DETENTION/CONTROL ∧ FINE=100–500% COUPON-VALUE;
    AMOUNT=HUGE ⇒ PENALTY=2–7Y IMPRISONMENT ∧ FINE=100–500% COUPON-VALUE
  CLAUSE2: PROFITEERING TRAIN/SHIP-TICKETS; CIRC=SERIOUS ⇒ PENALTY=≤3Y IMPRISONMENT/DETENTION/CONTROL ∧ FINE=100–500% COUPON-VALUE

ARTICLE-228: PURPOSE=PERSONAL-GAIN ∧ VIOLATE LAND-MANAGEMENT-LAWS VIA ILLEGAL TRANSFER/PROFITEERING LAND-USE-RIGHTS;
  CIRC=SERIOUS ⇒ PENALTY=≤3Y IMPRISONMENT/DETENTION ∧ FINE=5–20% ILLEGAL-GAIN;
  CIRC=PARTICULARLY-SERIOUS ⇒ PENALTY=3–7Y IMPRISONMENT ∧ FINE=5–20% ILLEGAL-GAIN

ARTICLE-229:
  SUBJECT: INTERMEDIARY-ORG-PERSONNEL (ASSET-ASSESSMENT/CERTIFICATE-EXAM/ACCOUNTING/AUDITING/LEGAL-SERVICES)
  ACT1: INTENTIONALLY PROVIDE FALSE-CERTIFICATES; CIRC=SERIOUS ⇒ PENALTY=≤5Y IMPRISONMENT/DETENTION ∧ FINE
  ACT2: EXTORT/ILLEGALLY-ACCEPT MONEY/GOODS FOR ABOVE-CRIME; CIRC=SERIOUS ⇒ PENALTY=≤5Y IMPRISONMENT/DETENTION ∧ FINE
  ACT3: SERIOUSLY-IRRESPONSIBLE ISSUING CERTIFICATES INCONSISTENT-WITH-FACTS; CIRC=SERIOUS-CONSEQUENCE ⇒ PENALTY=≤3Y IMPRISONMENT/DETENTION ∧ OPTIONAL-FINE

ARTICLE-230: AVOID COMMODITY-INSPECTION ∧ UNAUTHORIZED SALE/USE IMPORTED-GOODS OR UNINSPECTED EXPORT;
  CIRC=SERIOUS ⇒ PENALTY=≤3Y IMPRISONMENT/DETENTION ∧ OPTIONAL-FINE

ARTICLE-231: UNIT COMMITS CRIMES [221–230] ⇒ PENALTY=FINE; DIRECTLY-RESPONSIBLE-PERSONNEL ⇒ PUNISHED PER ARTICLE-STIPULATIONS

H2: CHAPTER-IV CRIMES INFRINGING RIGHTS OF PERSON ∧ DEMOCRATIC RIGHTS OF CITIZENS

ARTICLE-232: INTENTIONAL-KILLING ⇒ PENALTY=DEATH/LIFE-IMPRISONMENT/≥10Y IMPRISONMENT;
  CIRC=RELATIVELY-MINOR ⇒ PENALTY=3–10Y IMPRISONMENT

ARTICLE-233: NEGLIGENT-HOMICIDE ⇒ PENALTY=3–7Y IMPRISONMENT;
  CIRC=RELATIVELY-MINOR ⇒ PENALTY=≤3Y IMPRISONMENT; OTHER-STIPULATIONS APPLY

ARTICLE-234: INTENTIONAL-INJURY ⇒ PENALTY=≤3Y IMPRISONMENT/DETENTION/CONTROL
